title: Features: Dirt Devil Featherlite® Bagless Upright UD70100
transcripts: Well let's quickly review the key features on your dirt devil. Upright vacuum cleaner. There's a comfort handle grip the removable dirt cup has a quick release bottom for easy emptying and a removable air director for easy cleaning below the dirt cup is a removable filter cartridge with a reusable foam filter and a reusable pleated filter. It is important to clean the filter after every use and replace the filter every six months depending on use above floor cleaning attachments include a hose a dusting brush and a combination extension wand and crevice tool. The power cord stores neatly on the back and has a quick cord release there's a foot activated handle release and a foot activated on off switch.
